wikipedia_page.main: George Harvey Idris Harding (born 12 October 1996) is an English cricketer. He made his List A debut for Durham in the 2017 Royal London One-Day Cup on 3 May 2017. He made his first-class debut for Durham in the 2017 County Championship on 26 May 2017.
